    <descript>
      <abstract>This cultural polygon layer represents structures or impervious areas in Prince William County. Descriptions of type codes can be found in the Prince William County Data Dictionary.</abstract>
      <purpose>The purpose of this layer is to graphically represent cultural features as polygons. These features can include but are not limited to Commercial and Non-commercial Structures, Parking Lots and Recreation Areas. </purpose>
      <supplinf>Any determination of topography or contours or any depiction of physical improvements, property lines or boundaries is for general information only and shall not be used for the design modification or construction of improvements to real property or for flood plain determination.</supplinf>
